---

<section id="architecture" class="py-16 relative">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-8 reveal"
    >
      <div>
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sky-200 text-xs tracking-wide uppercase mb-4"
        >
          Architecture Diagram
        </div>
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading tracking-tight text-white"
        >
          System Architecture
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4 max-w-2xl">
          Placeholder for the final architecture diagram. This area will later
          show the end-to-end flow between telemetry collection, processing,
          orchestration, and coordination components.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="glass-soft rounded-3xl border border-dashed border-white/15 p-6 sm:p-10 reveal"
    >
      <div
        class="min-h-70 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(56,189,248,0.14),transparent_55%),linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.04),rgba(255,255,255,0.02))] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6"
      >
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-sky-500/10 border border-sky-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-300"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="1.8"
              d="M4 6h6v6H4V6zm10 0h6v6h-6V6zM4 16h6v2H4v-2zm10-4h6v6h-6v-6z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">
          Architecture diagram placeholder
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-3 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          The finalized diagram can be inserted here later. It should illustrate
          the telemetry pipeline, orchestration logic, and the communication
          path between cluster nodes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
